joxy

Class JoxySliderUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.plaf.ComponentUI
      • javax.swing.plaf.SliderUI
        • javax.swing.plaf.basic.BasicSliderUI
          • joxy.JoxySliderUI

  • public class JoxySliderUI
extends BasicSliderUI
    Joxy's UI delegate for the JSlider.

    The JoxySliderUI supports animations for the focus state (not yet the hovered state). See JoxyButtonUI for more details.

    Author:
    Thom Castermans, Willem Sonke
